    <div class="price-table-wrap">
      <table class="price-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Repair Type</th><th>Labor Range</th><th>What&rsquo;s Typically Involved</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Gas burner won&rsquo;t ignite <span class="gas-badge">GAS · MOST COMMON</span></div><div class="repair-desc">One or more surface burners won&rsquo;t light</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$280</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ igniter if needed (often none)</div></td>
            <td>Spark igniter, spark electrode, boilover cleaning. Gas pressure check included. All burners tested before leaving.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Gas burner flame uneven or too low <span class="gas-badge">GAS</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Weak flame, goes out, won&rsquo;t hold at low setting</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$175&ndash;$340</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ valve or cap if needed</div></td>
            <td>Burner cap misalignment (often free fix), gas valve, orifice cleaning, sealed burner assembly on luxury brands</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Gas all burners clicking constantly <span class="gas-badge">GAS</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Non-stop clicking even when all burners off</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$280</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ module if failed</div></td>
            <td>Ignition module short from moisture, igniter switch failure. Usually resolves with drying or is a simple switch replacement.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Electric radiant element not heating</div><div class="repair-desc">One or more zones dead on smooth-top electric cooktop</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$300</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ element or switch</div></td>
            <td>Radiant element replacement, infinite switch (heat control) failure, ribbon connector issue</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Electric element won&rsquo;t turn off</div><div class="repair-desc">Zone stuck on high, uncontrolled heat</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$175&ndash;$320</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ infinite switch</div></td>
            <td>Infinite switch failure &mdash; fire hazard. Priority repair. Same-day service recommended.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Cracked glass surface</div><div class="repair-desc">Glass cooktop cracked, chipped, or shattered</div></td>
