            <td>Induction coil failure, control board zone failure, IGBT transistor replacement. Requires power electronics knowledge to diagnose correctly.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Induction touch panel unresponsive <span class="induction-badge">INDUCTION</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Controls don&rsquo;t respond, display issues, error codes</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$200&ndash;$400</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ control board or panel</div></td>
            <td>Touch control board, display panel, wiring harness. We confirm board vs. panel vs. software error before ordering parts.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Induction error codes / shutting off <span class="induction-badge">INDUCTION</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Unit shuts off mid-cook, persistent error codes</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$200&ndash;$380</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ parts per diagnosis</div></td>
            <td>Overtemperature shutoff (often ventilation issue &mdash; no parts needed), temperature sensor, control board fault</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="luxury-row">
            <td><div class="repair-type">Wolf / Thermador / Miele <span class="luxury-badge">LUXURY</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Gas, electric, or induction &mdash; all failure types</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$280&ndash;$560+</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ OEM parts (premium pricing)</div></td>
            <td>Proprietary sealed burner systems (gas), premium induction electronics (Miele FlexInduction), custom control modules</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Diagnostic fee</div><div class="repair-desc">Service call + full diagnosis &middot; gas includes pressure check</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$89</div><div class="price-parts-note">Applied to repair</div></td>
            <td>Applied to labor total when you approve. Gas calls include pressure check and leak test. Induction diagnosis includes power electronics check.</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="table-note"><strong>All prices are labor only.</strong> Parts quoted separately. Gas calls include safety check. Induction calls include power electronics diagnosis. Quote before we start; invoice matches the quote. 90-day warranty on parts and labor.</p>
  </div>
</section>

